\c 13
\s Dhavhidhi anovimba
\s nokubatsira kwaMwari
\ Kumutungamiriri wokuimba;
\s Pisarema raDhavhidhi
\p
\v 1 Jehovha muchandikanganwa nokusingaperi kusvikira rini?
\s Muchandivanzira chiso chenyu kusvikira riniko?
\p
\v 2 Ndichafunga mano mumweya mangu kusvikira rini,
\s Ndine shungu pamwoyo pangu zuva rimwe nerimwe?
\s Muvengi wangu achandikurira kusvikira rini?
\p
\v 3 Rangarirai, mundipindure, Jehovha Mwari wangu;
\s Vhenekerai meso angu, ndirege kuvata hope dzokufa;
\p
\v 4 Muvengi wangu arege kuti, "Ndamukunda;"
\s Vadzivisi vangu varege kufara kana ndichizununguka.
\p
\v 5 Asi ndakavimba nenyasha dzenyu; Mwoyo wangu uchafara nokuponesa kwenyu;
\p
\v 6 Ndichaimbira Jehovha,
\s Nokuti akandiitira zvakanaka.
